### Javadocs & Solr Refguide
# __root/docs.lucene.apache.org/content/ is a special alias added by INFRA-19439, so we can refer to stuff in other places like SVN

RewriteRule ^(core|solr)/(\d+_\d+_\d+\b.*)$ __root/docs.lucene.apache.org/content/$1/$2 [PT]
RewriteRule ^solr/guide/(\d+_\d+\b.*)$ __root/docs.lucene.apache.org/content/solr/guide/$1 [PT]

